---
layout: base.njk
title: Changelog
---

<div class="hero">
  <h1 class="hero-title">Changelog</h1>
  <p class="hero-description">Release history of the collective-self system. Each version is a new MOTD ── the message that greets you when you connect.</p>
</div>

<hr class="section-divider">

{% for m in motd | reverse %}
<div class="terminal-box">
  <span class="terminal-box-title">v{{ m.version }} ── {{ m.date }}{% if m.current %} ── CURRENT{% endif %}</span>

<span class="label">{{ m.title }}</span>

<span class="sys">COLLECTIVE-SELF SYSTEM v{{ m.version }}</span>
<span class="sys">{{ m.connection }}</span>
<span class="sys">────────────────────────────────────</span>
{% include m.file %}<span class="sys">────────────────────────────────────</span>
<span class="prompt">▶</span> <span class="output">{{ m.command }}</span>

</div>
{% endfor %}
